@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zmtupl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(0.75)
    v1 = wp.sin(((tmp + 0.21 + tmp + 0.43) + (tmp + 0.49 / v1 + 0.75)))
    tmp = v1
    v2 = (v2 - tmp)
    v1 = wp.abs(0.69)
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v2 + 0.15)) / (wp.abs(v1 + 0.25) * wp.cos(v2 + 0.57)))
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.abs(0.95))
    v0 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.26 + tmp + 0.62)) + wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.97)))
    data[tid] = v0
